						               													<description>You think you know music? You think you can recognize songs faster than your friends? Then prove it and Grab the Mike! The only game that tests your music knowledge, reaction time and singing ability (or lack thereof)! Cards are drawn to select music genres; whatever genre is revealed is then played on your favorite streaming radio app or played on your smart home speaker.  Once the song starts, the first person that recognizes the song Grabs the Mike and attempts to sing at least the first two lines of the song correctly. Know more than the first two lines? Then keep singing for more points.  The rest of the group judges you on how well you know the song and awards points accordingly. Or, use a pass chip and make any other player attempt said song. In the deck there are also spoiler cards, where you may have to sing a duet or the whole group may have to get up and sing as a choir. Fast-paced, addictive party game that is fun for all ages!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
